Description_lang: Fyrakk rends the fabric of the Emerald Dream, inflicting $425481s1 Fire damage to all players and opening up a rift into the Firelands.Searing heat pours through the rift, inflicting $419217s1 Fire damage to all players every $s1 sec for $420644d and pulling players towards its location. Players farther from the rift receive less damage.Players drawn beneath the rift are $@spellname425483.
